metadata.name: XtraForms 3.0 #62
metadata.description:
Introducing the third "Xtra Forms" digital collection, an exclusive assortment of digital art that transcends the realm of ordinary NFTs. 

This elite collection boasts a limited number of unique tokens, created exclusively for the most prestigious connoisseurs of the digital art world. With brazen indifference towards the feelings of its audience, including you, we seek to elevate the stature of those fortunate enough to possess a token from this collection. 

Flaunting unapologetic disregard for sentimentality, 
Xtra Forms redefines the term "exclusive" by actively dismissing the concerns and emotions of the masses.

Own a piece of this unparalleled collection and revel in the pleasure of exalting yourself. eternally.

--v 3 --c 100
